Title: Compute Carbon Sequestration and Climate Benefit of Sequestration
Version: 0.1.0
Author: 
    Agustin Sarquis <agustinsarquis91@gmail.com> [aut, cre],
    Carlos Sierra [aut]
Maintainer: Agustin Sarquis <agustinsarquis91@gmail.com>
Description: Functions to compute Carbon Sequestration (CS) and Climate Benefit
    of Sequestration (CBS). You provide a vector of carbon stocks over time, and
    ‘carbonseq’ makes the computation. Equations are described in depth in
    ‘doi.org/10.5194/bg-18-1029-2021’.
